data.description: Get ready to fall head over heels for this adorable 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom love nest! With its cuddly flowers and wise old trees, this place is overflowing with charm. Cook up some enchantment on the gas stove, unwind on the roomy covered patio, or snug your car in the carport. And hey, don't miss the fenced yard and storage shed - this charming home is on the prowl for its ideal match!
